  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed new roof storey would disrupt both the front and rear roofscapes of a terrace which has had no other roof storeys added. This would go against the expectation of Policy D4 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002 that extensions should be sympathetic both to the building extended and its surroundings. It would also run counter to the guidance contained in the Islington Urban Design Guide 2006, which seeks to preserve the unity of the terrace by protecting what is currently a well-defined roofline."
